{"tid":1112692,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"論盡新歡舊愛 馬國明：心穎近乎完美「她能安撫我」","createTime":"2019-04-17T13:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T14:59:15.000Z","uid":209890,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"121b1c2aeaa5c1289ddcc7f08123d4be89e63e13","tid":1112692,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"「她能安撫我」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSkcJMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSkcJMg.jpg&h=4a25d76a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n「我跟心穎的感情綫幾得意，但最終是一段淒美的苦戀，心穎的角色主動單純，在爾虞我詐的後宮可謂『死咗都唔知咩事』，任三恕就是被她的清純善良吸引。我與心穎拍對手戲時當然有被劇組人員取笑，連拍咀戲時也特別多人圍觀，不過我們都投入在角色中，不感尷尬。其實大家開玩笑在所難免，惟有豁達點跟他們一起玩，因為你愈避忌人家便愈想玩你，有時心穎主動『大』他們，他們便冇聲出了。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們到橫店拍外景日對夜對，了解當然加深，跟間中食飯睇戲的感覺截然不同，因為每個人工作到又熱又攰時，最真實的一面自然會出來。好似我也會因此發脾氣，但只限自己忟自己，匿埋一邊默不作聲，這時心穎就能安撫我，因為她很愛笑，樣子又傻更更，看到她便能放鬆一下繃緊的情緒。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfKdtcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfKdtcW.jpg&h=46cd8830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUBWqZB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUBWqZB.jpg&h=485b5ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/748597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F748597&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=aaa57c63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F748597&h=63710a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/748597</a>"},{"pid":"53bab65ac6d29ac6d7accac7a1aa72622cb238da","tid":1112692,"uid":34256,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"溝完一個木獨老實樣<br />\n玩厭左就搞另一個木獨老實樣嘅有婦之夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a168